description: Doctor Psycho’s control over the quiet haven Bekka found has brought her worst nightmare to life. Routing him might bring her the peace she sought, but there’s no guarantee that she can defeat his monstrous creations.
name: The Dream - Part 3 of 3

description: “Nine Days” part 1 of 3! It takes nine days, the gods say, for an anvil to fall to Earth from Olympus. But what happens when it strikes the world of men? Wonder Woman doesn’t want to find out...
